title: A Little Apology.
body: I would like to apologize for taking so long between parts. The truth is, since my summer job is coming to it’s end (it’ll probably be done by the end of this month), I’ve been getting a lot more days off. And having worked a lot over the past few months, it basically took me out of my sails, so I’ve been probably the least productive in a while. And for that, I am sorry. I do have the draft for Part 3, but it’s not even halfway done, I don’t think, yet. It’ll get done, rest assured. Until then, I apologize.
